Package com.symbian.commdb.ui

Class Summary
BrokenLinks This class defines a form which displays information regarding the broken table entry links of the CommDB database, if any.
BrokenLinksCellRenderer This class implements a colour cell renderer for the table which displays all broken table entry references
BrokenLinksTableModel This class defines the table model used for displaying the table entry parameters which refer to table entries (links) which no longer exist (broken) | Qualified Parameter Name | Qualified Broken Table Entry Name | | | |
Editor The CommDB Editor main program
ExtensionFilter This is a general purpose file filter class to be used by the editor to open files.
InformationTable This class defines a table which displays the CommDB information
InformationTableModel This class defines the table model used for displaying some information of any CommDB database.
MainMenu This class implements the main menu form of the CommDB Editor
PropertiesCellEditor This class defines a cell table editor used for allowing the editing of the parameter values of any CommDB table entry column
PropertiesCellRenderer This class implements a colour cell renderer for the CommDB table properties column
PropertiesTableModel This class defines the table model used for editing the properties of any CommDB table.
TableEditor This form implements an editor for the entries of a CommDB table
Usage This class defines a form which displays information regarding the usage of this application
